  "original_title": "4 \u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd ! \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Get the 4th covid vaccine! Health Ministry's request to the public",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "There is a risk of a global resurgence of the corona virus. Many countries are now focusing on implementing health measures.",
        "In this case, there are chances of corona infection spreading again in the country and in order to control it, the Ministry of Health has requested the people to get the fourth vaccination properly in the first phase.",
        "Director General of Health Services Asela Gunawardena said this while speaking at a press conference held at the Government Information Department on Tuesday 05th.",
        "Due to the global spread of Covid infection, many countries were paralyzed. Sri Lanka has managed to contain the spread of Covid-19 amid various challenges.",
        "The main reason for this is that the covid infection vaccines have been properly administered to the people of the country. Because of that we were able to recover from it.",
        "In this case, the risk of covid infection is emerging in many countries. The countries concerned are re-imposing restrictions related to Covid.",
        "Accordingly, those who have received regular covid vaccinations should also receive the 4th vaccination. Also those who have not received the first two doses of covid vaccine and get the 3rd dose regularly.",
        "Accordingly, the 4th covid vaccine for covid prevention can be obtained through the nearby hospitals and vaccination centers. He said that by discussing this with the concerned health workers, go there and get it at the right time."
      ],
